spec_data.Name: perl-MooseX-Types-Stringlike
spec_data.Description:
This module provides a more general version of the Str type. If coercions are
enabled, it will accept objects that overload stringification and coerces them
into strings.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:08:00 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Moose type constraints for strings or string-like objects
